Test::WWW::Mechanize::Mojo - Test::WWW::Mechanize for Mojo

Test::WWW::Mechanize::Mojo is a module to test Mojo applications using
Test::WWW::Mechanize and WWW::Mechanize.

It is based on Test::WWW::Mechanize::Catalyst .

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Test::WWW::Mechanize::Mojo

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Test-WWW-Mechanize-Mojo/

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Test::WWW::Mechanize::Mojo

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Test::WWW::Mechanize::Mojo

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Test::WWW::Mechanize::Mojo

